{"tid":896194,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[警世] 美容狗面孔召喚","createTime":"2018-11-09T20:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T12:03:32.000Z","uid":69844,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"df3667928038ceb1a8cc84411b0446b02d5ef5c0","tid":896194,"uid":69844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T20:07:04.000Z","msg":"有鑑於美容狗喺交友app愈來愈多<br />\n<br />\n以下慣用手段:<br />\n<br />\n1. 話自己做marketing firm or agent<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 先欺騙感情再send相話自己做緊facial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 話好多男仔都會做facial，好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/035152_c94dc7ae98c89ccfa464ccc715ea1c7f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F035152_c94dc7ae98c89ccfa464ccc715ea1c7f.png&h=0e118445&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/035154_38d9cf8211face9bb452f6a7773c2b45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F035154_38d9cf8211face9bb452f6a7773c2b45.png&h=9e1cf4e5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/10/035155_ecc44e7e5064660e3914e3154fba3fbd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F10%2F035155_ecc44e7e5064660e3914e3154fba3fbd.png&h=f06bd5b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望各巴打放低遇過嘅美容狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以免再有人受害<br />\n<br />\n亦都等識佢嘅人認清佢真面目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\"